iots|year=2020|border=2}}\" |Previous team\n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|New England Patriots|year=2020|border=2}}\" |Date signed\n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|New England Patriots|year=2020|border=2}}\" |Contract\n|- style=\"background:#ff9\"\n|[[Defensive tackle|DT]]\n|[[Beau Allen]]\n|[[2020 Tampa Bay Buccaneers season|Tampa Bay Buccaneers]]\n|March 20, 2020<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://rostermon.com/player/3876/|title=Beau Allen|website=rostermon.com|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref>\n|2 years, $7 million<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.spotrac.com/nfl/new-england-patriots/beau-allen-14635/|title=Beau Allen|last=Spotrac.com|website=Spotrac.com|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#ff9\"\n|[[Safety (gridiron football position)|S]]\n|[[Adrian Phillips]]\n|[[2019 Los Angeles Chargers season|Los Angeles Chargers]]\n|March 21, 2020<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://rostermon.com/player/4462/|title=Adrian Phillips|website=rostermon.com|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref>\n|2 years, $6 million<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.spotrac.com/nfl/new-england-patriots/adrian-phillips-15335/|title=Adrian Phillips|last=Spotrac.com|website=Spotrac.com|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#ff9\"\n|[[Fullback (gridiron football)|FB]]\n|[[Danny Vitale]]\n|[[2019 Green Bay Packers season|Green Bay Packers]]\n|March 21, 2020<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://rostermon.com/player/6179/|title=Danny Vitale|website=rostermon.com|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref>\n|1 year, $1.3 million<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.spotrac.com/nfl/new-england-patriots/dan-vitale-19151/|title=Dan Vitale|last=Spotrac.com|website=Spotrac.com|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#ff9\"\n|[[Wide receiver|WR]]\n|[[Damiere Byrd]]\n|[[2019 Arizona Cardinals season|Arizona Cardinals]]\n|March 23, 2020<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://rostermon.com/player/5608/|title=Damiere Byrd|website=rostermon.com|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref>\n|1 year, $1.4 million<ref>{